---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="歴史">

<style is:global>
.page-header { max-width: var(--wide); margin: 0 auto; padding: 4rem 1.25rem 3rem; border-bottom: 0.5px solid var(--paper-dark); }
.page-eyebrow { font-size: 10px; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 0.18em; color: var(--ink-faint); text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
.page-title { font-size: clamp(28px,4vw,44px); font-weight: 400; color: var(--ink); letter-spacing: 0.06em; line-height: 1.3; margin-bottom: 1.25rem; }
.page-desc { font-size: 15px; font-weight: 300; color: var(--ink-light); line-height: 1.9; max-width: 560px; letter-spacing: 0.02em; }
.page-count { margin-top: 1.5rem; font-size: 11px; color: var(--ink-faint); letter-spacing: 0.08em; }

.tag-link { font-size: 10px; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 0.1em; padding: 2px 8px; border-radius: 2px; transition: opacity 0.2s; display: inline-block; cursor: pointer; }
.tag-link:hover { opacity: 0.65; }
.tag-entry { background: var(--paper-mid); color: var(--ink-light); border: 0.5px solid var(--paper-dark); }
.tag-issue  { background: var(--ink); color: var(--paper); }

.article-grid-cat { max-width: var(--wide); margin: 0 auto; padding: 3rem 0 6rem; display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0,1fr)); gap: 0; }

.article-list { display: none; }
.article-list-item { display: flex; gap: 1rem; align-items: stretch; padding: 1rem; border-bottom: 0.5px solid var(--paper-dark); transition: background 0.2s; }
.article-list-item:first-child { border-top: 0.5px solid var(--paper-dark); }
.article-list-item:active { background: var(--paper-mid); }
.list-img { width: 80px; flex-shrink: 0; overflow: hidden; background: var(--paper-dark); border-radius: 3px; }
.list-img img { width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover; display: block; }
.list-body { flex: 1; min-width: 0; display: flex; flex-direction: column; }
.list-title { font-size: 14px; font-weight: 400; color: var(--ink); line-height: 1.2; letter-spacing: 0.02em; margin-bottom: 0.4rem; display: -webkit-box; -webkit-line-clamp: 2; -webkit-box-orient: vertical; overflow: hidden; }
.list-lead { font-size: 11px; font-weight: 300; color: var(--ink-light); line-height: 1.65; letter-spacing: 0.01em; display: -webkit-box; -webkit-line-clamp: 2; -webkit-box-orient: vertical; overflow: hidden; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
.list-meta { display: flex; align-items: flex-end; gap: 6px; flex-wrap: wrap; margin-top: auto; }
.list-date { font-size: 10px; color: var(--ink-faint); letter-spacing: 0.06em; margin-left: auto; }

@media (max-width: 900px) { .article-grid-cat { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0,1fr)); } }
@media (max-width: 600px) {
  .page-header { padding: 2.5rem 1.25rem 2rem; }
  .article-grid-cat { display: none; }
  .article-list { display: block; }
}
</style>

<div class="page-header">
  <div class="page-eyebrow">Category</div>
  <h1 class="page-title">歴史</h1>
  <p class="page-desc">江戸の都市建設、明治の近代化、戦後の復興——日本の歴史は山と木材なしには語れない。過去の山と都市の関係から、今を読み解く。</p>
  <div class="page-count">5 articles</div>
</div>

<!-- PC: グリッド -->
<div class="article-grid-cat">
  <a href="#" class="article-card fade-in">
    <div class="card-img"><img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1503174971373-b1f69850bded?w=800&q=70" alt=""></div>
    <div class="card-body">
      <div class="card-title">江戸の建築を支えた、奥多摩の森の話</div>
      <div class="card-lead">現代の住宅地として知られる奥多摩は、かつて江戸の建築需要を支えた木材の産地だった。</div>
      <div class="card-meta"><span class="tag-link tag-entry">歴史</span><span class="tag-link tag-issue">山</span><span class="card-date">2024.02.28</span></div>
    </div>
  </a>
  <a href="#" class="article-card fade-in">
    <div class="card-img"><img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1512917774080-9991f1c4c750?w=800&q=70" alt=""></div>
    <div class="card-body">
      <div class="card-title">木曽ヒノキ、その盛衰と現在</div>
      <div class="card-lead">かつて「木曽のヒノキは幕府の御用材」と呼ばれた。過剰伐採と保護の歴史が、現代の木曽の山を作った。</div>
      <div class="card-meta"><span class="tag-link tag-entry">歴史</span><span class="tag-link tag-issue">木材</span><span class="card-date">2024.01.15</span></div>
    </div>
  </a>
  <a href="#" class="article-card fade-in">
    <div class="card-img"><img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1558618666-fcd25c85cd64?w=800&q=70" alt=""></div>
    <div class="card-body">
      <div class="card-title">明治の製材業が日本の山を変えた</div>
      <div class="card-lead">蒸気鋸の導入により、日本の製材業は劇的に変わった。その変化が森に何をもたらしたのか。</div>
      <div class="card-meta"><span class="tag-link tag-entry">歴史</span><span class="tag-link tag-issue">林業</span><span class="card-date">2023.12.10</span></div>
    </div>
  </a>
  <a href="#" class="article-card fade-in">
    <div class="card-img"><img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1545324418-cc1a3fa10c00?w=800&q=70" alt=""></div>
    <div class="card-body">
      <div class="card-title">吉野杉400年の歴史を歩く</div>
      <div class="card-lead">吉野の山に杉が植えられたのは江戸初期。400年にわたる人工林の歴史は、日本最長の林業史でもある。</div>
      <div class="card-meta"><span class="tag-link tag-entry">歴史</span><span class="tag-link tag-issue">山</span><span class="card-date">2023.10.25</span></div>
    </div>
  </a>
  <a href="#" class="article-card fade-in">
    <div class="card-img"><img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1503174971373-b1f69850bded?w=800&q=70" alt=""></div>
    <div class="card-body">
      <div class="card-title">尾鷲ヒノキと海運、近代日本の木材流通史</div>
      <div class="card-lead">紀伊半島の尾鷲から木材が大阪へ。海の道を使った木材流通が、近代日本の都市建設を支えた。</div>
      <div class="card-meta"><span class="tag-link tag-entry">歴史</span><span class="tag-link tag-issue">木材</span><span class="card-date">2023.09.12</span></div>
    </div>
  </a>
</div>

